prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D botanical illustration for a greeting card. A humorous and vibrant San Diego beach scene. In the foreground, cartoon versions of the couple from the reference photo are having a playful moment. Lao Lao, on the left, is laughing and attempting to steal a comically oversized boba tea from Jordan, on the right, who is holding it up just out of her reach with a playful, smiling expression. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue sweatshirt and black pants. Jordan is wearing a brown hoodie and dark pants. The boba tea is in a large cup with tapioca pearls visible at the bottom. The sand is dotted with little illustrated elements like starfish and seashells. The background features stylized, gentle ocean waves characteristic of a San Diego beach, with a few sailboats in the distance under a sunny sky. The entire scene is framed by a delicate border of lush tropical botanicals, like monstera leaves and hibiscus flowers, in soft greens and cheerful colors. Centered in the middle of the design, beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script says, "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" The overall mood is bright, charming, and full of personality.
